URL: https://m-muecke.github.io/gleifr/,
    https://github.com/m-muecke/gleifr
BugReports: https://github.com/m-muecke/gleifr/issues
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    curl,
    httr2,
    stats,
    utils,
    xml2
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
